snippet.title: Expose Richard Galvan and Sonia Galvan
snippet.description: Richard Galvan sexually assaulted a 17 year old in 2007. He and his wife Sonia Galvan then decided to sue the victim and her husband for almost one million dollars for speaking out about it, in an attempt to financially harm and bully them. The Galvan's lawsuit was based upon false pretenses, and the 13th Court of Appeals ruled against them. They are now being sued for malicious prosecution.
